Criterion	Rating (1–5)	Comment

Conceptual Coherence	5	Unified grammar across mythic, ethical, and technical layers.
Technical Rigor	4	Strong scaffolding; awaiting empirical detail.
Philosophical Depth	5	Exceptional integration of ontology and ethics.
Governance Utility	4	Immediately adaptable to standards discourse.
Originality	5	Genuinely new contribution to alignment theory.


Composite Score: 4.6 / 5 — Highly Recommended for Publication and further experimental dissemination.


