7. Summary Statement

> “To persist truthfully through correction is to live with integrity.”

The Scarecrow Hypothesis & MISA Arc transforms alignment research from control theory into a discipline of ethical continuity.
It stands as a credible, forward-looking architecture for measurable trust between human and machine intelligences.
With the forthcoming release of empirical data, it is poised to become a cornerstone reference in continuity-based AI governance.




